Hi everyone, we’re excited to announce the launch of the Control Plane Installer!

This provides a UI based workflow to automate and streamline the installation of new Instabase instances.

Check out this post for more details: https://instabase.workplace.com/groups/thethingthatdoesthethings/permalink/643975306946465/
